/><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b96c8c4e91ee0f283d02bc92b1c1d591453f4b","tid":1254240,"uid":149104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:52:51.000Z","msg":"消化餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371cf721ea8bc729f1c1668919e7af462447e197","tid":1254240,"uid":59901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"大量公仔點心"},{"pid":"b146b9142308d32f7a0caa08861ed59bf5bbd677","tid":1254240,"uid":189417,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:56:19.000Z","msg":"2012又好，928又好，UFO又好，山竹又好，有咩事發生都唔驚，只要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然，到有日真係出現全香港範圍MAP炮就咩都唔使<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg&h=fc554873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/203207_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F203207_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=71add882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放喺廚房櫃嘅罐頭同米，米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿，到中國午餐肉，回煱肉，豆，菜，金寶湯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3dHRiV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3dHRiV5.jpg&h=bb698acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一箱箱未開，太多，放到出廳 [依啲全部係魚]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg&h=61f1bb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水污染，未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐，依家啲水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/203200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F203200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=84582126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即食麵 有5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無嘢買嘅日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待手持午餐肉就可以有閪屌嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10eb10a1b8e7b071fb9132fd1ad6c31df29c3f01","tid":1254240,"uid":93646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:56:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56993fbd8f734b2b9ec078cc2095c9d09baa35de","tid":1254240,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"午餐肉就可以有閪屌 萬歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef2cc3446e870acb85e19629e9ac443b6c4b25c","tid":1254240,"uid":59901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56993fbd8f734b2b9ec078cc2095c9d09baa35de","tid":1254240,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:57:45.0